'''艾林·奧圖爾''' {{post-nominals|country=CAN|PC|CD|MP}}（{{lang|en|Erin O'Toole}}，{{bd|1973年|1月22日}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，2020年-22年間任職[[加拿大保守黨|聯邦保守黨]]黨魁和[[加拿大官方反對黨領袖|官方反對黨領袖]]。他從2012年起擔任[[加拿大眾議院|眾議院]][[杜林選區|杜林選區]]議員，2015年1月至11月在[[加拿大總理|總理]][[史蒂芬·哈珀|哈珀]][[加拿大內閣|內閣]]中出任退伍軍人事務部長。奧圖爾曾兩度競逐聯邦保守黨黨魁職務，2017年黨魁選舉中敗予[[安德魯·熙爾|熙爾]]名列第三，2020年黨魁選舉則告捷。從政前他曾先後任職加拿大空軍軍官和律師。

==早年及個人生活==
奧圖爾的母親莫莉（{{lang|en|Molly}}）於二戰後從英國遷居加拿大並任職教師，父親約翰則具有愛爾蘭裔血統，家族在加拿大定居數代<ref name="CMV"/><ref>https://openparliament.ca/politicians/erin-otoole/?page=98</ref>，而約翰本人則在加拿大[[通用汽車|通用汽車]]的[[安大略省|安大略省]][[杜林區|杜林區]][[奧沙華|奧沙華]]廠房工作<ref name="auto">{{Cite news|last1=van Bilsen |first1=Jonathan |title=The Story Behind The Person - Erin O'Toole |url=http://www.thestandardnewspaper.ca/the-story-behind-the-person---jonathan-van-bilsen/the-story-behind-the-person-erin-otoole |website=The Standard Newspaper |accessdate=2018-11-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103091952/http://www.thestandardnewspaper.ca/the-story-behind-the-person---jonathan-van-bilsen/the-story-behind-the-person-erin-otoole#|archivedate=2018-11-03 }}</ref>。約翰一度調派至[[魁北克省|魁北克省]][[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]]，艾林則於1973年在當地出生<ref name="Parlinfo"/>，但年幼時一家遷回奧沙華<ref name="auto"/>。艾林九歲喪母後，一家遷居安省佩里港（{{lang|en|Port Perry}}），他在當地上小學和中學<ref name="auto"/>。他其後再與家人遷至寶文圍（{{lang|en|Bowmanville}}），1991年從寶文圍中學畢業<ref name="about">{{cite web|url=https://erinotoolemp.com/about/|title=About Erin|publisher=艾林·奧圖爾個人網站|accessdate=2020-08-24}}</ref>。

奧圖爾於2000年與莉貝卡（{{lang|en|Rebecca}}）結婚，兩人育有兩名子女<ref>{{cite web |last1=Pessian |first1=Parvaneh |title=Durham MP Erin O'Toole launches Conservative leadership bid in Bowmanville |url=https://www.durhamregion.com/news-story/6911571-durham-mp-erin-o-toole-launches-conservative-leadership-bid-in-bowmanville/ |website=DurhamRegion.com |accessdate=1 November 2018}}</ref>。父親約翰曾於1995年至2014年間出任[[安大略省議會|安大略省議會]]杜林選區議員<ref>{{Cite web|title=John O'Toole {{!}} Legislative Assembly of Ontario|url=https://www.ola.org/en/members/all/john-otoole|access-date=2020-07-03|website=www.ola.org|language=en}}</ref>。

==從軍及律師事業==
奧圖爾於1991年到安省[[金斯頓_(安大略省)|京士頓]]的{{le|加拿大皇家軍事學院|Royal Military College of Canada}}修讀歷史和政治學，1995年從該校獲取文學士學位後加入[[加拿大軍隊|加拿大軍隊]]空防司令部（現[[皇家加拿大空軍|皇家加拿大空軍]]），軍階為[[少尉|少尉]]<ref name="auto2">{{cite web |last1=Levitz |first1=Stephanie |title=Five things to know about new veterans Affairs Minister Erin O'Toole |url=https://ipolitics.ca/2015/01/05/five-things-to-know-about-new-veterans-affairs-minister-erin-otoole/ |website=iPolitics.ca |accessdate=1 November 2018}}</ref>並派駐安省[[特倫頓空軍基地|特倫頓空軍基地]]，期間協調搜救任務<ref name="auto"/>。他後到[[緬尼托巴省|緬尼托巴省]][[溫尼伯|溫尼伯]]的第17翼基地進行航空員訓練<ref name="auto2"/>，學成後於1997年派駐[[新斯科舍省|新斯科舍省]]希爾沃特（{{lang|en|Shearwater}}）的第12翼基地，出任第423中隊的[[SH-3海王直昇機|CH-124海王直升機]]戰術航空員，進行海上監視、搜救和海軍支援等任務<ref name="auto2"/>，期間並晉升為上尉。他於2000年改編預備役，任職第406中隊的訓練官並操作飛行模擬器<ref name="auto"/>，期間到[[哈利法斯|哈利法斯]]的[[戴爾豪斯大學|戴爾豪斯大學]]修讀法律<ref name="about"/>。他服役12年後獲頒{{le|加拿大軍隊獎章|Canadian Forces' Decoration}}，並因在海上拯救受傷漁夫而獲發[[西科斯基飛機公司|西科斯基直升機]]救援獎<ref name="auto"/>。

奧圖爾於2003年從戴爾豪斯大學獲取法學士學位後返回安省<ref name="about"/>，於[[多倫多|多倫多]]的斯泰克曼艾略特（{{lang|en|Stikeman Elliott}}）商務律師事務所實習後獲該行聘用。他於2006年出任[[寶潔|寶潔]]的内部律師<ref name="CMV">{{cite web |title=Interview Series: Erin O'Toole |url=https://www.canadianmuslimvote.ca/cpc_interview_series_erin_o_toole |website=The Canadian-Muslim Vote |accessdate=1 November 2018}}</ref>，2011年則轉職希南布雷奇（{{lang|en|Heenan Blaikie}}）律師事務所<ref>{{cite web |title=Heenan Blaikie lawyer takes aim at replacing Bev Oda in Parliament |url=http://lawandstyle.ca/law/heenan-blaikie-lawyer-takes-aim-at-replacing-bev-oda-in-parliament/ |website=Precedent |accessdate=1 November 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Gray |first1=Jeff |title=The inside story of Heenan Blaikie's frantic final days |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/the-inside-story-of-heenan-blaikies-frantic-final-days/article34344309/ |website=The Globe and Mail |accessdate=1 November 2018}}</ref>。

==政治生涯==
[[加拿大保守黨|聯邦保守黨]]籍的[[加拿大眾議院|眾議院]][[杜林選區|杜林選區]]議員小田（{{lang|en|Bev Oda}}）於2012年請辭，觸發議席補選。奧圖爾於同年5月宣布競逐該選區的保守黨候選人資格<ref>{{cite web |last1=Erman |first1=Boyd |title=Bay Street lawyer eyes Bev Oda's seat |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/streetwise/bay-street-lawyer-eyes-bev-odas-seat/article4391358/ |website=The Globe and Mail}}</ref>，並於同年8月自動獲取候選人提名<ref>{{cite news|last1=O'Meara|first1=Jennifer|title=Erin O'Toole to be Conservative candidate in Durham|url=https://www.durhamregion.com/news-story/3507378-erin-o-toole-to-be-conservative-candidate-in-durham/ |publisher=DurhamRegion.com |newspaper=Oshawa This Week}}</ref>。在同年11月26日舉行的杜林選區議席補選，奧圖爾以50.7%得票率輕易當選，首度晉身國會<ref>{{cite news|title=Tories and NDP hold on to seats in tight byelections |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/tories-and-ndp-hold-on-to-seats-in-tight-byelections-1.1138587?cmp=rss|website=CBC News|date=2012-11-26|accessdate=2020-08-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Hall |first1=Chris |title=Erin O'Toole thoroughly dominates Durham |url=https://www.durhamregion.com/news-story/3510019-erin-o-toole-thoroughly-dominates-durham/ |website=DurhamRegion.com}}</ref>。他任期初段只擔當[[後座議員|後座議員]]，到2013年9月則獲任為國際貿易部長法斯特（{{lang|en|Ed Fast}}）的國會秘書<ref>{{cite web |title=Parliamentary Roles - Erin O'Toole |url=http://www.ourcommons.ca/Parliamentarians/en/members/Erin-OToole(72773)/Roles |website=Parliament of Canada}}</ref>。[[加拿大總理|總理]][[史蒂芬·哈珀|哈珀]]於2015年改組[[加拿大內閣|內閣]]，奧圖爾獲任為退伍軍人事務部長<ref>[http://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2015/01/05/pm-announces-changes-ministry "PM Announces Change to the Ministry"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150105195452/http://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2015/01/05/pm-announces-changes-ministry |date=2015-01-05 }} January 5, 2015</ref>。

奧圖爾在[[2015年加拿大聯邦大選|2015年聯邦大選]]中以45%得票率連任杜林選區眾議院議員<ref>{{cite web |title=Durham Riding stays blue with Erin O'Toole: 2015 federal election results |url=https://www.durhamregion.com/news-story/5957078-durham-riding-stays-blue-with-erin-o-toole-2015-federal-election-results/ |website=DurhamRegion.com}}</ref>。然而，保守黨在該屆大選落敗，哈珀遂辭任黨魁。奧圖爾宣布競逐臨時黨魁職務<ref>{{cite news|title=Erin O'Toole, ex-Veterans Affair minister, to seek Conservative interim leadership |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-interim-leader-conservatives-1.3288843 |website=CBC News|first=Jennifer|last=Ditchburn|publisher=The Canadian Press|date=2015-10-26|accessdate=2020-08-24}}</ref>，但敗於[[羅娜·安布羅斯|安布羅斯]]；安布羅斯隨後任命奧圖爾為官方反對黨公共安全評議員<ref>{{cite web |last1=Harris |first1=Kathleen |title=Rona Ambrose chosen as interim Conservative leader |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/conservative-interim-leader-vote-1.3306152 |website=CBC News|date=2015-11-05|accessdate=2020-08-24}}</ref>。

[[File:Meeting_with_Erin_O'Toole_-_Rencontre_avec_Erin_O'Toole_(37309864436).jpg|thumb]]

2016年10月14日，奧圖爾宣布參與翌年舉行的聯邦保守黨黨魁選舉<ref>{{cite web |last1=Pessian |first1=Parvaneh |title=Durham MP Erin O'Toole launches Conservative leadership bid in Bowmanville |url=https://www.durhamregion.com/news-story/6911571-durham-mp-erin-o-toole-launches-conservative-leadership-bid-in-bowmanville/ |website=DurhamRegion.com}}</ref>。[[安德魯·熙爾|熙爾]]最終當選黨魁，奧圖爾則名列第三<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cpac.ca/en/conservative-leadership-results/|title=Conservative Leadership: The Results|date=May 29, 2017|website=CPAC|accessdate=Oct 22, 2019}}</ref>。熙爾後於2017年8月任命奧圖爾為外交、貿易及發展評議員<ref>{{cite web |last1=O'Meara |first1=Jennifer |title=O'Toole named Conservative shadow minister for foreign affairs |url=https://www.durhamregion.com/news-story/7530558-o-toole-named-conservative-shadow-minister-for-foreign-affairs/ |website=DurhamRegion.com |date=2017-08-31 |accessdate=2020-08-24 }}</ref>。

[[彭建邦|彭建邦]]於2018年辭任[[安大略進步保守黨|安大略進步保守黨]]黨魁後，奧圖爾一度考慮競逐該職<ref>{{cite web |last1=Lunn |first1=Susan |last2=Tasker |first2=John |title=Conservative MP Erin O'Toole considering run for Ontario PC leadership |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/otoole-ontario-pc-leadership-1.4512368 |website=CBC News}}</ref>，但他後來表示支持[[葉麗雅|葉麗雅]]參選<ref>{{cite web |last1=Fitzpatrick |first1=Meagan |title=Erin O'Toole takes pass on Ontario PC leadership, endorses Christine Elliott |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-o-toole-takes-pass-on-ontario-pc-leadership-endorses-christine-elliott-1.4516404 |website=CBC News}}</ref>。

====保守黨黨魁====
[[2019年加拿大聯邦大選|2019年聯邦大選]]中奧圖爾連任眾議院議員，但保守黨則再度敗予[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]。面對黨內壓力，熙爾於同年末宣布辭任保守黨黨魁<ref>{{cite web |title=Canada Conservative leader in surprise resignation |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-50762474 |website=BBC News |date=12 December 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Rabson |first1=Mia |first2= |title=Conservative party in disarray over Scheer private school controversy |url=https://www.nationalobserver.com/2019/12/15/news/conservative-party-disarray-over-scheer-private-school-controversy |website=National Observer |language=en |date=15 December 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=MacCharles |first1=Tonda |title=Andrew Scheer quitting as Conservative leader amid controversy |url=https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal/2019/12/12/andrew-scheer-to-step-down-as-conservative-party-leader.html |website=thestar.com |language=en |date=12 December 2019}}</ref>，但留任至新任黨魁當選為止<ref>{{cite web |last1=Connolly |first1=Amanda |title=Conservative Leader Andrew Scheer resigns, vows to stay on until new leader chosen |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/6288286/andrew-scheer-resignation/ |website=Global News}}</ref>。奧圖爾於2020年1月宣布競逐黨魁<ref>{{cite web |last1=Levitz |first1=Stephanie |title=Erin O'Toole announces bid for Conservative leadership in Alberta |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/6466394/erin-otoole-conservative-leadership-race/ |website=Global News}}</ref>，並於同年8月舉行的黨魁選舉中壓倒[[彼得·麥凱|麥凱]]等人，當選保守黨黨魁<ref name=leadership>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-23|title=Erin O'Toole wins Conservative Party of Canada leadership on 3rd ballot|url=https://www.cp24.com/news/erin-o-toole-wins-conservative-party-of-canada-leadership-on-3rd-ballot-1.5075658|access-date=2020-08-24|website=CP24|language=en}}</ref>。奧圖爾成功游說黨內[[社會保守主義|社會保守派]]人士－包括黨魁候選人斯隆（{{lang|en|Derek Sloan}}）和劉易斯（{{lang|en|Leslyn Lewis}}）的支持者－在黨魁選舉中把他列為第二或第三選擇，被視為他的致勝關鍵之一<ref name=leadership/><ref name="ts082520">{{cite news |last1=Boutilier |first1=Alex |title=After riding social conservative support to leadership victory, Erin O'Toole reaffirms he's 'pro-choice' |url=https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal/2020/08/25/erin-otoole-reaffirms-pro-choice-stance-says-hell-defend-rights-as-conservative-leader.html |access-date=December 28, 2020 |work=Toronto Star |publisher=Torstar |date=August 25, 2020}}</ref>。

奧圖爾就任黨魁後表示將集中應對[[2019冠狀病毒病加拿大疫情|冠狀病毒疫情]]，而促使自由黨[[少數政府|少數政府]]倒台則並非他的當前急務<ref name="global083020">{{cite news |last1=Bensadoun |first1=Emerald |title=Conservative Leader O'Toole says triggering fall election 'not my priority' |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/7305699/conservative-erin-otoole-fall-election/ |access-date=August 31, 2020 |work=Global News |publisher=Corus Entertainment |date=August 30, 2020 |archive-date=August 30, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830233717/https://globalnews.ca/news/7305699/conservative-erin-otoole-fall-election/ }}</ref><ref name="cbc090220b">{{cite news |last1=Tasker |first1=John Paul |title=Conservative Leader Erin O'Toole downplays talk of a fall federal election |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-fall-election-1.5709569 |access-date=September 2, 2020 |work=CBC News |publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |date=September 2, 2020 |archive-date=September 2, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902200514/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-fall-election-1.5709569 }}</ref>。他於2020年12月重申該立場，謂應待疫情過後才舉行大選<ref name="ctv121320">{{cite news |last1=Aiello |first1=Rachel |title=O'Toole eyes post-pandemic election, vows to keep pushing feds on COVID-19 in meantime |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/o-toole-eyes-post-pandemic-election-vows-to-keep-pushing-feds-on-covid-19-in-meantime-1.5229337 |access-date=December 15, 2020 |work=CTV News |publisher=Bell Media |date=December 13, 2020}}</ref>，但也稱大選若舉行的話保守黨亦準備就緒<ref name=cbc090220b/>。當選黨魁後的奧圖爾立場較黨魁選舉期間溫和，因此惹來黨內部分人士批評，亦有黨員憂慮他會放棄部分保守派主張（如反對[[碳税|碳税]]）<ref name="np030621">{{cite news |last1=Platt |first1=Brian |title=As tensions rise in Conservative caucus, Erin O'Toole's leadership is put to the test |url=https://nationalpost.com/news/politics/as-tensions-rise-in-conservative-caucus-erin-otooles-leadership-put-to-the-test |access-date=March 13, 2021 |work=National Post |publisher=Postmedia |date=March 6, 2021}}</ref><ref name="ts030221">{{cite news |last1=Boutilier |first1=Alex |title=Will Erin O'Toole embrace a carbon tax? Some of his MPs are worried he will, insiders say |url=https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal/2021/03/02/will-erin-otoole-embrace-a-carbon-tax-some-of-his-mps-are-worried-he-will-insiders-say.html |access-date=March 13, 2021 |work=Toronto Star |publisher=Torstar |date=March 2, 2021}}</ref>。奧圖爾其後雖有認理黨內批評，但表示保守黨需具勇氣變革才可吸納新選民從而擊敗自由黨，因此堅持其溫和路線<ref name="star082121">{{cite news |last1=Reynolds |first1=Christopher |title=O'Toole acknowledges some Conservatives 'frustrated' over carbon pricing plan |url=https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal-election/2021/08/21/otoole-pledges-to-hike-disability-supports-by-doubling-annual-supplement.html |access-date=August 21, 2021 |work=Toronto Star |publisher=Torstar |date=August 21, 2021}}</ref><ref name="np031921">{{cite news |last1=Platt |first1=Brian |title=Conservative Party must have 'the courage to change,' Erin O'Toole tells party convention |url=https://nationalpost.com/news/politics/the-conservative-party-must-have-the-courage-to-change-erin-otoole-tells-party-convention |access-date=March 19, 2021 |work=National Post |publisher=Postmedia |date=March 19, 2021}}</ref>。

[[2021年加拿大聯邦大選|2021年聯邦大選]]，保守黨面對右翼[[加拿大人民黨|人民黨]]挑戰。奧圖爾於競選期尾段向人民黨支持者拉票，謂人民黨會分薄右翼票源，最終只惠及自由黨<ref name=cbc092021/>。保守黨在該屆大選再次敗予自由黨，但得票率則高於自由黨，而奧圖爾本人則再度在杜林選區連任眾議院議員<ref name="ctv092121">{{cite news |last1=Turnbull |first1=Sarah |title=Conservatives fail to dethrone Liberals |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/federal-election-2021/conservatives-fail-to-dethrone-liberals-1.5593607 |access-date=September 21, 2021 |work=CTV News |publisher=Bell Media |date=September 21, 2021}}</ref><ref name="popvote21">{{cite news |last1=Flanagan |first1=Ryan |title=Liberals return to Alberta, and 5 other surprises in the election results |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/federal-election-2021/liberals-return-to-alberta-and-5-other-surprises-in-the-election-results-1.5593768 |access-date=September 21, 2021 |work=CTV News |publisher=Bell Media |date=September 21, 2021}}</ref>。他於大選當晚表示會留任黨魁<ref name="cbc092021">{{cite news |last1=Tunney |first1=Catharine |title=Conservative Leader Erin O'Toole sticks with moderate message despite falling short |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-election-1.6182500 |access-date=September 21, 2021 |work=CBC News |publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |date=September 20, 2021}}</ref>，但其後保守黨内部則就奧圖爾去留出現分歧<ref name="ctv092621">{{cite news |last1=Turnbull |first1=Sarah |title=Conservatives divided on fate of O'Toole, as party's MPs call for unity |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/conservatives-divided-on-fate-of-o-toole-as-party-s-mps-call-for-unity-1.5599886 |access-date=September 26, 2021 |work=CTV News |publisher=Bell Media |date=September 26, 2021}}</ref><ref name="cbc092321">{{cite news |last1=Tasker |first1=John Paul |title=Conservatives divided on what to do about Erin O'Toole after election loss |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/conseratives-split-erin-otoole-1.6187155 |access-date=September 26, 2021 |work=CBC News |publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |date=September 23, 2021}}</ref>。

2022年1月31日，卡加利地區保守黨籍國會議員本森（{{lang|en|Bob Benzen}}）致函保守黨黨團主席里德（{{lang|en|Scott Reid}}）要求舉行黨魁檢討選舉，並獲35名保守黨籍國會議員署名支持<ref>{{cite news |last1=Tasker |first1=John |title=Conservative caucus revolt triggers vote on Erin O'Toole's leadership |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-leadership-review-caucus-1.6334491 |website=CBC News |access-date=2 February 2022 |date=31 January 2022}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=35保守黨國會議員連署 迫使奧圖爾面臨信任投票 |url=https://www.singtao.ca/5540865/2022-02-01/post-35%e4%bf%9d%e5%ae%88%e9%bb%a8%e5%9c%8b%e6%9c%83%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e9%80%a3%e7%bd%b2-%e8%bf%ab%e4%bd%bf%e5%a5%a7%e5%9c%96%e7%88%be%e9%9d%a2%e8%87%a8%e4%bf%a1%e4%bb%bb%e6%8a%95%e7%a5%a8/ |publisher=《星島日報》加東版 |access-date=2022-02-05 |date=2022-02-01 }}</ref>。經過秘密投票後，保守黨黨團以73票對45票通過罷免奧圖爾<ref>{{Cite news|last=Tasker|first=John Paul|date=February 2, 2022|title=Conservative MPs vote to remove Erin O'Toole as leader|work=CBC News|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/otoole-leadership-vote-1.6336336|access-date=February 2, 2022}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=February 2, 2022|title=Caucus votes Erin O'Toole out as Conservative party leader|url=https://www.cp24.com/news/caucus-votes-erin-o-toole-out-as-conservative-party-leader-1.5764199|access-date=February 2, 2022|website=CP24|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last1=Boutilier|first1=Alex|last2=Connolly|first2=Amanda|date=February 2, 2022|title=Erin O'Toole ousted as Conservative leader after caucus revolt|url=https://globalnews.ca/news/8588503/erin-otoole-ousted-in-caucus-revolt/|access-date=February 2, 2022|website=Global News|language=en-CA}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Taylor |first1=Stephanie |title=Erin O'Toole voted out as leader by Conservative MPs |url=https://nationalpost.com/pmn/news-pmn/canada-news-pmn/canadian-press-newsalert-erin-otoole-voted-out-as-conservative-leader-by-mps |access-date=February 2, 2022 |work=National Post |date=February 2, 2022 |language=en}}</ref>。奧圖爾遂於同年2月2日即時卸任黨魁<ref>{{Cite news|last=Levitz|first=Stephanie|date=February 2, 2022|title=Erin O'Toole removed as Conservative leader in vote by MPs|language=en-CA|work=The Toronto Star|url=https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal/2022/02/02/erin-otoole-makes-final-appeal-to-keep-his-job.html|access-date=February 2, 2022|issn=0319-0781}}</ref>，但留任杜林選區眾議院議員<ref>{{cite news |title=奧圖爾遭罷免 女副手暫接掌 |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20220203/vaa1h_r.htm |publisher=《明報》加西網 |access-date=2022-02-05 |date=2022-02-03 }}</ref>。

